longBusinessSummary: Isofol Medical AB (publ) operates as a clinical stage biotech company. The company develops arfolitixorin, which is in phase Ib/II clinical trial for the treatment of metastatic colorectal cancer. Isofol Medical AB (publ) was incorporated in 2008 and is based in Gothenburg, Sweden.
